To generate a fat JAR - to use the embedded tomcat
1). Run as maven clean
2). Run as maven install
4). go to target dir and copy the flightreservation-*.jar

To generate a war 
1). in the pom.xml change packaging to war
2). main app should extend SpringBootServletInitializer
3). Override the configure method
4). do a maven update
5). Run as maven clean
6). Run as maven install
4). go to target dir and copy the flightreservation-*.war